data.title: James Ramsay MacDonald — An ‘Aristocrat’ among Plain Men?
data.meta_description: No person ever did more to help build up a new political party than James Ramsay MacDonald. Few subsequently did more to damage their own creation. That was the essential tragedy of his life.
